Claim Rewrds

We are happy to announce that to further support the growth of Idle Cyber. We share rewards for community up to 1750000 AFK rewards and you are one of the lucky who get Idle Cyber.

2088, after Judge Day, the world has changed. Humans build big walls to defend themselves from the Cyborgs that want to bring destruction to humanity. You command a squad of mutants called Cyber Defense, hold the wall, kill all these Cyborgs and conquer giant Bosses. All in an idle frontier-defense game: Idle Cyber.
Play Game

Adventure in the post-apocalypse world of Idle Cyber - the Hero Collection Defense RPG with stunning graphics.

Play 2 Earn

Form your Cybers, use right skills at the right time to defend the base and win to earn Idle Cyber tokens and valuable NFT assets.

Game Fi

Trade your NFTs on a full-stack Marketplace or upgrade them in Idle Cyber system to maximize their value and make profits through DeFi features. Specially player can trade upgraded NFTs.

1. What is Idle Cyber?
Idle Cyber is a P2E model idle game. Huge content with unlimited levels and PvP mode, the game is a new kind of frontier defense and RPG heroes collection mixed in blockchain technology. The attractive game structure and social features of play-to-earn model make players keep playing.
2. Which Blockchain will the game be developed on?

The game will be developed on the Binance Smart Chain (BSC).
SmartContract : 0xbA0B46F556633Bd742546E4F37D66D416753003B

3. How was this game Idle Cyber created?

Idle Cyber is produced and published by BeeMob Studio that has been incubated and trained by Google in Singapore since 2018. Based on traditional game Cyber War whose every detail is completely suitable for a NFT game, Idle Cyber was conceived then developed right after Cyber War’s launching.

4. What will Idle Cyber offer?

At Idle Cyber, we equal and satisfy 2 main needs of users: Revenue and Experience.

We guarantee play-to-earn for all users (expected ROI in 1 month at launching, then 1~3 months). The mechanism that strengthens token holding efficiency helps to increase the token price gradually. 

At the same time, we carefully analyze user behaviors to come up with the most appropriate UX/UI in order to satisfy every little feeling of each user.

5. Why should you have a NFT box?

Users who open the box will have the advantage of getting an SS rank hero that allows faster PVE and higher climbing on PVP rank.

6. What is the main role of coins in Idle Cyber’s ecosystem?

We use 2 tokens in the game: AFK and IDLE.  

  • $AFK: Governance token used for buying NFTs, staking, evolution, trading & rewards.
  • $IDLE: 2nd token used for  items/gears purchasing, heroes/items/gears updates, trading & rewards.
